                   8080.itch.io
                   
                   
Pixel Art Tower Defence!

You accidentally fall into a dungeon, this triggered a
silent alarm on a spaceship full of aliens. They are
monitoring you and launching a full-scale attack to
protect their secret earth base! You can't escape, only
way is forward... Good Luck!


                     Have fun !!!


Game is entirely written in m/c


In game:

         Arrow - move cursor, 
         Space - action,
         
         USB Gamepad support, D-pad,A,Start,Back




Requirements:

Apollo Vampire V4
AmigaOS 3.x / ApolloOS
640x360


Install:
Drag drawer/folder to your HDD, no assignments needed.



